{"tid":1953663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄增500例單日新高  普京接觸染疫醫師","createTime":"2020-04-01T09:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T12:16:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8fada987d4cffb41ab80bd95c4e670e8afd653cf","tid":1953663,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:57:21.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯新冠肺炎確診數一天內新增500例，連續第7天創下單日通報新高紀錄，全國累計確診數增至2337例，並有18名患者不治。上周陪同俄國總統普亭參觀莫斯科主要醫院的醫師，被診斷出罹患新冠肺炎。克里姆林宮對此表示，普亭已接受檢測，一切正常。<br />\n<br />\n克宮：總統檢測一切正常<br />\n<br />\n普亭（Vladimir Putin）24日參觀俄國最大的新冠肺炎患者專門醫院科穆納爾卡醫院（Kommunarka），並和醫師普羅佐科（Denis Protsenko）交談。普羅佐科是院內首席醫師，他31日在自己的臉書上發文證實確診。根據電視畫面顯示，兩人交談時都沒有戴防護裝備。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯新聞社報導，克里姆林宮表示，普亭定期接受新冠病毒檢測，並且「一切正常」。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4461536</code></pre>"},{"pid":"8a0457d520a05d3e0e8bca2ab94c3a308b905000","tid":1953663,"uid":78971,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"普京一中<br />\n雜種狗都冇情講"},{"pid":"2b362bdcb4b4eafb0e0c0ecc236e480d70d2e41a","tid":1953663,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:59:50.000Z","msg":"想做俄羅斯人<br />\n普京大帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50832e6fb2417e694b9cfd8a58ee11519f0c014d","tid":1953663,"uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"支那攬炒全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf0c6df407f35add9b35d3164c10f2885f523ff","tid":1953663,"uid":65074,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:00:48.000Z","msg":"中國嘅武漢病毒如果整得死普京同金仔<br />\n都舟廿對世界有返少少正面影響"},{"pid":"1077f7722da177913f7c2261edfc377e2f26e347","tid":1953663,"uid":155095,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2019/06/GettyImages-1148400307.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.li